segtool
=======

A utility to calculate segments based upon questionnaire results


Installation
============

# Clone the segtool repository & cd into it
# Run $ python setup.py sdist
# Copy the tar.gz file from the /dist directory into your project
# pip install the tar.gz file
# You should now be able to use segtool functions, e.g.

>>> from segtool import segtool
>>> segtool.get_segment_title(5)
'Practical Travellers'


Testing
=======

Add application src to the PYTHONPATH:
    $ PYTHONPATH=`pwd`/segtool

Run the tests:
    $ python test/segtool_test.py
